{"tid":1645893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"4女子在深水埗嘉頓山被人用刀襲擊受傷 施襲男子在逃","createTime":"2019-10-11T05:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T13:04:17.000Z","uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"363984ba9f44ed76510b13bbfcfc99cbb0b7a683","tid":1645893,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深水埗嘉頓山發生傷人案，4名女子被人用刀襲擊受傷，有人一度昏迷，後來轉為清醒，施襲男子仍然在逃。<br />\n<br />\n案發在早上約10時，途人報案指一名男子持刀襲擊3名女子，男子逃走期間再襲擊多一名女子，有人胸和背部受刀傷，分別送往瑪嘉烈醫院和伊利沙伯醫院治理，4名傷者都沒有財物損失。<br />\n<br />\n警方正追緝一名男子，中等身材、約1.6米高，身穿T裇和長褲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485533-20191011.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485533-20191011.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=aa8562ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485533-20191011.htm&h=b8378d06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485533-20191011.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b1ce1369ac5102726e0c3292cfeac9483c9e2098","tid":1645893,"uid":299984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3db65af3bcfc74d27c8f6b5da7839936c02c6169","tid":1645893,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4591b9cc8f174e355344b53fac600aa710a8a142","tid":1645893,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深水埗手足小心</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"070c80d013477f3d63e6f5f74672ead5e83e9244","tid":1645893,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"深水埗嘉頓山發生傷人案，4名女子被人用刀襲擊受傷。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">截至下午2時，兩人情況危殆，兩人嚴重，暫時未有人被捕。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n案發在早上約10時，途人報案指一名男子持刀襲擊3名行山人士，疑兇逃走期間再襲擊另一名女子。4名傷者年齡介乎於50至56歲。有人胸和背部中刀，分別送往瑪嘉烈醫院和伊利沙伯醫院治理，4人都沒有財物損失。<br />\n<br />\n警方正追緝一名涉案男子，他中等身材、約1.6米高，案發時身穿T裇及長褲。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485603-20191011.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485603-20191011.htm&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=117ead20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485603-20191011.htm&h=f1e7d6cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485603-20191011.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6e4ff2dad8f22b168a744115bedd22b096046376","tid":1645893,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一名男子持刀襲擊3名行山人士，疑兇逃走期間再襲擊另一名女子</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e7ab97624f34cfcad5bae64ac6fafe363f4dc028","tid":1645893,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"[置頂]仲做浮屍推理？集氣搵佢男朋友或友人出黎好過啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屌 我無用呀 要推撚到識佢嘅人先有方法搵到真相呀<br />\n9推理真係無用架...<br />\n推上去呀 再唔搵人就連唯一線索都會被消失"},{"pid":"76f0997124b538630c084a96889c2337253f38bd","tid":1645893,"uid":102356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110e97cd3d223cac2e602d1878ae9c38618a47e6","tid":1645893,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"好似冇乜跟